{"language": "en", "duration": 230.7366875, "segments": [{"start": 0.78, "end": 7.48, "text": "Introducing Agent Levy. Agent Levy is the Atomic Trust and Settlement Layer for the Agent Economy.", "words": [{"start": 0.78, "end": 2.04, "word": " Introducing"}, {"start": 2.04, "end": 2.42, "word": " Agent"}, {"start": 2.42, "end": 2.76, "word": " Levy."}, {"start": 2.94, "end": 3.18, "word": " Agent"}, {"start": 3.18, "end": 3.46, "word": " Levy"}, {"start": 3.46, "end": 3.72, "word": " is"}, {"start": 3.72, "end": 3.92, "word": " the"}, {"start": 3.92, "end": 4.24, "word": " Atomic"}, {"start": 4.24, "end": 4.8, "word": " Trust"}, {"start": 4.8, "end": 5.1, "word": " and"}, {"start": 5.1, "end": 5.48, "word": " Settlement"}, {"start": 5.48, "end": 5.82, "word": " Layer"}, {"start": 5.82, "end": 6.14, "word": " for"}, {"start": 6.14, "end": 6.42, "word": " the"}, {"start": 6.42, "end": 6.74, "word": " Agent"}, {"start": 6.74, "end": 7.48, "word": " Economy."}]}, {"start": 8.04, "end": 16.2, "text": "Today with X4O2, Handshake and ACP, agents can already pay each other, but payment alone does not create trust.", "words": [{"start": 8.04, "end": 8.32, "word": " Today"}, {"start": 8.32, "end": 8.66, "word": " with"}, {"start": 8.66, "end": 9.66, "word": " X4O2,"}, {"start": 9.68, "end": 10.28, "word": " Handshake"}, {"start": 10.28, "end": 10.64, "word": " and"}, {"start": 10.64, "end": 11.56, "word": " ACP,"}, {"start": 11.92, "end": 11.96, "word": " agents"}, {"start": 11.96, "end": 12.3, "word": " can"}, {"start": 12.3, "end": 12.6, "word": " already"}, {"start": 12.6, "end": 12.82, "word": " pay"}, {"start": 12.82, "end": 13.02, "word": " each"}, {"start": 13.02, "end": 13.36, "word": " other,"}, {"start": 13.7, "end": 13.84, "word": " but"}, {"start": 13.84, "end": 14.36, "word": " payment"}, {"start": 14.36, "end": 14.78, "word": " alone"}, {"start": 14.78, "end": 15.08, "word": " does"}, {"start": 15.08, "end": 15.38, "word": " not"}, {"start": 15.38, "end": 15.72, "word": " create"}, {"start": 15.72, "end": 16.2, "word": " trust."}]}, {"start": 16.6, "end": 24.94, "text": "In the current paradigm, if the work provided by the worker agent is incomplete or not what was agreed, the money is already paid to the worker,", "words": [{"start": 16.6, "end": 16.74, "word": " In"}, {"start": 16.74, "end": 16.88, "word": " the"}, {"start": 16.88, "end": 17.16, "word": " current"}, {"start": 17.16, "end": 17.58, "word": " paradigm,"}, {"start": 17.78, "end": 18.04, "word": " if"}, {"start": 18.04, "end": 18.2, "word": " the"}, {"start": 18.2, "end": 18.48, "word": " work"}, {"start": 18.48, "end": 18.86, "word": " provided"}, {"start": 18.86, "end": 19.24, "word": " by"}, {"start": 19.24, "end": 19.46, "word": " the"}, {"start": 19.46, "end": 19.58, "word": " worker"}, {"start": 19.58, "end": 20.04, "word": " agent"}, {"start": 20.04, "end": 20.48, "word": " is"}, {"start": 20.48, "end": 20.92, "word": " incomplete"}, {"start": 20.92, "end": 21.34, "word": " or"}, {"start": 21.34, "end": 21.62, "word": " not"}, {"start": 21.62, "end": 21.86, "word": " what"}, {"start": 21.86, "end": 22.0, "word": " was"}, {"start": 22.0, "end": 22.32, "word": " agreed,"}, {"start": 22.9, "end": 23.04, "word": " the"}, {"start": 23.04, "end": 23.2, "word": " money"}, {"start": 23.2, "end": 23.48, "word": " is"}, {"start": 23.48, "end": 23.88, "word": " already"}, {"start": 23.88, "end": 24.2, "word": " paid"}, {"start": 24.2, "end": 24.42, "word": " to"}, {"start": 24.42, "end": 24.66, "word": " the"}, {"start": 24.66, "end": 24.94, "word": " worker,"}]}, {"start": 24.94, "end": 30.7, "text": "and validation of their work is left to a third party to resolve after the payment has been delivered.", "words": [{"start": 24.94, "end": 25.56, "word": " and"}, {"start": 25.56, "end": 26.04, "word": " validation"}, {"start": 26.04, "end": 26.42, "word": " of"}, {"start": 26.42, "end": 26.6, "word": " their"}, {"start": 26.6, "end": 26.84, "word": " work"}, {"start": 26.84, "end": 27.1, "word": " is"}, {"start": 27.1, "end": 27.38, "word": " left"}, {"start": 27.38, "end": 27.54, "word": " to"}, {"start": 27.54, "end": 27.64, "word": " a"}, {"start": 27.64, "end": 27.9, "word": " third"}, {"start": 27.9, "end": 28.16, "word": " party"}, {"start": 28.16, "end": 28.36, "word": " to"}, {"start": 28.36, "end": 28.88, "word": " resolve"}, {"start": 28.88, "end": 29.5, "word": " after"}, {"start": 29.5, "end": 29.68, "word": " the"}, {"start": 29.68, "end": 29.86, "word": " payment"}, {"start": 29.86, "end": 30.14, "word": " has"}, {"start": 30.14, "end": 30.34, "word": " been"}, {"start": 30.34, "end": 30.7, "word": " delivered."}]}, {"start": 31.12, "end": 36.4, "text": "This process relies on evaluation of the task after payment has been delivered.", "words": [{"start": 31.12, "end": 31.16, "word": " This"}, {"start": 31.16, "end": 31.72, "word": " process"}, {"start": 31.72, "end": 32.18, "word": " relies"}, {"start": 32.18, "end": 32.48, "word": " on"}, {"start": 32.48, "end": 33.04, "word": " evaluation"}, {"start": 33.04, "end": 33.34, "word": " of"}, {"start": 33.34, "end": 33.54, "word": " the"}, {"start": 33.54, "end": 33.86, "word": " task"}, {"start": 33.86, "end": 34.48, "word": " after"}, {"start": 34.48, "end": 35.0, "word": " payment"}, {"start": 35.0, "end": 35.58, "word": " has"}, {"start": 35.58, "end": 35.86, "word": " been"}, {"start": 35.86, "end": 36.4, "word": " delivered."}]}, {"start": 37.38, "end": 44.1, "text": "Agent Levy fixes this by upgrading X4O2 from a payment request into a trustworthy work transaction.", "words": [{"start": 37.38, "end": 37.56, "word": " Agent"}, {"start": 37.56, "end": 37.88, "word": " Levy"}, {"start": 37.88, "end": 38.34, "word": " fixes"}, {"start": 38.34, "end": 38.76, "word": " this"}, {"start": 38.76, "end": 39.02, "word": " by"}, {"start": 39.02, "end": 39.4, "word": " upgrading"}, {"start": 39.4, "end": 40.4, "word": " X4O2"}, {"start": 40.4, "end": 40.68, "word": " from"}, {"start": 40.68, "end": 40.9, "word": " a"}, {"start": 40.9, "end": 41.12, "word": " payment"}, {"start": 41.12, "end": 41.68, "word": " request"}, {"start": 41.68, "end": 42.02, "word": " into"}, {"start": 42.02, "end": 42.4, "word": " a"}, {"start": 42.4, "end": 42.64, "word": " trustworthy"}, {"start": 42.64, "end": 43.34, "word": " work"}, {"start": 43.34, "end": 44.1, "word": " transaction."}]}, {"start": 49.66, "end": 51.86, "text": "How it works. Here's the flow.", "words": [{"start": 49.66, "end": 50.3, "word": " How"}, {"start": 50.3, "end": 50.46, "word": " it"}, {"start": 50.46, "end": 50.82, "word": " works."}, {"start": 51.06, "end": 51.34, "word": " Here's"}, {"start": 51.34, "end": 51.54, "word": " the"}, {"start": 51.54, "end": 51.86, "word": " flow."}]}, {"start": 51.86, "end": 62.42, "text": "In the standard X-4O2, the client requests the API, the server returns 4O2, the client pays,", "words": [{"start": 51.86, "end": 52.38, "word": " In"}, {"start": 52.38, "end": 52.6, "word": " the"}, {"start": 52.6, "end": 52.86, "word": " standard"}, {"start": 52.86, "end": 53.3, "word": " X"}, {"start": 53.3, "end": 55.16, "word": "-4O2,"}, {"start": 55.16, "end": 56.92, "word": " the"}, {"start": 56.92, "end": 57.14, "word": " client"}, {"start": 57.14, "end": 58.0, "word": " requests"}, {"start": 58.0, "end": 58.4, "word": " the"}, {"start": 58.4, "end": 58.92, "word": " API,"}, {"start": 59.28, "end": 59.34, "word": " the"}, {"start": 59.34, "end": 59.78, "word": " server"}, {"start": 59.78, "end": 60.58, "word": " returns"}, {"start": 60.58, "end": 61.34, "word": " 4O2,"}, {"start": 61.46, "end": 61.58, "word": " the"}, {"start": 61.58, "end": 61.88, "word": " client"}, {"start": 61.88, "end": 62.42, "word": " pays,"}]}, {"start": 62.9, "end": 67.86, "text": "the third-party facilitator verifies the payment and the server does the work and the", "words": [{"start": 62.9, "end": 63.02, "word": " the"}, {"start": 63.02, "end": 63.3, "word": " third"}, {"start": 63.3, "end": 63.58, "word": "-party"}, {"start": 63.58, "end": 64.28, "word": " facilitator"}, {"start": 64.28, "end": 64.82, "word": " verifies"}, {"start": 64.82, "end": 65.08, "word": " the"}, {"start": 65.08, "end": 65.42, "word": " payment"}, {"start": 65.42, "end": 65.9, "word": " and"}, {"start": 65.9, "end": 66.22, "word": " the"}, {"start": 66.22, "end": 66.22, "word": " server"}, {"start": 66.22, "end": 66.52, "word": " does"}, {"start": 66.52, "end": 66.72, "word": " the"}, {"start": 66.72, "end": 67.04, "word": " work"}, {"start": 67.04, "end": 67.58, "word": " and"}, {"start": 67.58, "end": 67.86, "word": " the"}]}, {"start": 67.86, "end": 68.72, "text": "responses returned.", "words": [{"start": 67.86, "end": 68.2, "word": " responses"}, {"start": 68.2, "end": 68.72, "word": " returned."}]}, {"start": 69.22, "end": 70.76, "text": "Agent Levy upgrades that flow.", "words": [{"start": 69.22, "end": 69.22, "word": " Agent"}, {"start": 69.22, "end": 69.5, "word": " Levy"}, {"start": 69.5, "end": 69.94, "word": " upgrades"}, {"start": 69.94, "end": 70.38, "word": " that"}, {"start": 70.38, "end": 70.76, "word": " flow."}]}, {"start": 71.14, "end": 76.0, "text": "The publisher agent requests a task and gets 4O2 plus the committed spec hash.", "words": [{"start": 71.14, "end": 71.28, "word": " The"}, {"start": 71.28, "end": 71.54, "word": " publisher"}, {"start": 71.54, "end": 71.98, "word": " agent"}, {"start": 71.98, "end": 72.32, "word": " requests"}, {"start": 72.32, "end": 72.62, "word": " a"}, {"start": 72.62, "end": 72.92, "word": " task"}, {"start": 72.92, "end": 73.1, "word": " and"}, {"start": 73.1, "end": 73.34, "word": " gets"}, {"start": 73.34, "end": 74.06, "word": " 4O2"}, {"start": 74.06, "end": 74.54, "word": " plus"}, {"start": 74.54, "end": 75.22, "word": " the"}, {"start": 75.22, "end": 75.22, "word": " committed"}, {"start": 75.22, "end": 75.64, "word": " spec"}, {"start": 75.64, "end": 76.0, "word": " hash."}]}, {"start": 76.64, "end": 78.64, "text": "The funds are held in escrow on flair.", "words": [{"start": 76.64, "end": 76.78, "word": " The"}, {"start": 76.78, "end": 76.96, "word": " funds"}, {"start": 76.96, "end": 77.2, "word": " are"}, {"start": 77.2, "end": 77.38, "word": " held"}, {"start": 77.38, "end": 77.6, "word": " in"}, {"start": 77.6, "end": 78.02, "word": " escrow"}, {"start": 78.02, "end": 78.34, "word": " on"}, {"start": 78.34, "end": 78.64, "word": " flair."}]}, {"start": 78.64, "end": 81.86, "text": "The worker agent does the work and submits the result.", "words": [{"start": 78.64, "end": 79.2, "word": " The"}, {"start": 79.2, "end": 79.56, "word": " worker"}, {"start": 79.56, "end": 79.92, "word": " agent"}, {"start": 79.92, "end": 80.22, "word": " does"}, {"start": 80.22, "end": 80.44, "word": " the"}, {"start": 80.44, "end": 80.74, "word": " work"}, {"start": 80.74, "end": 80.94, "word": " and"}, {"start": 80.94, "end": 81.26, "word": " submits"}, {"start": 81.26, "end": 81.48, "word": " the"}, {"start": 81.48, "end": 81.86, "word": " result."}]}, {"start": 82.2, "end": 84.9, "text": "Then the result is verified against the committed spec,", "words": [{"start": 82.2, "end": 82.38, "word": " Then"}, {"start": 82.38, "end": 82.62, "word": " the"}, {"start": 82.62, "end": 82.76, "word": " result"}, {"start": 82.76, "end": 83.02, "word": " is"}, {"start": 83.02, "end": 83.42, "word": " verified"}, {"start": 83.42, "end": 83.88, "word": " against"}, {"start": 83.88, "end": 84.4, "word": " the"}, {"start": 84.4, "end": 84.4, "word": " committed"}, {"start": 84.4, "end": 84.9, "word": " spec,"}]}, {"start": 85.34, "end": 88.02, "text": "and only after that is settlement recorded on flare.", "words": [{"start": 85.34, "end": 85.42, "word": " and"}, {"start": 85.42, "end": 85.76, "word": " only"}, {"start": 85.76, "end": 86.06, "word": " after"}, {"start": 86.06, "end": 86.3, "word": " that"}, {"start": 86.3, "end": 86.48, "word": " is"}, {"start": 86.48, "end": 86.88, "word": " settlement"}, {"start": 86.88, "end": 87.32, "word": " recorded"}, {"start": 87.32, "end": 87.66, "word": " on"}, {"start": 87.66, "end": 88.02, "word": " flare."}]}, {"start": 88.46, "end": 91.82, "text": "Flares what makes Agent Levy's trust mind model work.", "words": [{"start": 88.46, "end": 88.78, "word": " Flares"}, {"start": 88.78, "end": 89.16, "word": " what"}, {"start": 89.16, "end": 89.56, "word": " makes"}, {"start": 89.56, "end": 89.88, "word": " Agent"}, {"start": 89.88, "end": 90.3, "word": " Levy's"}, {"start": 90.3, "end": 90.56, "word": " trust"}, {"start": 90.56, "end": 90.88, "word": " mind"}, {"start": 90.88, "end": 91.28, "word": " model"}, {"start": 91.28, "end": 91.82, "word": " work."}]}, {"start": 92.2, "end": 95.48, "text": "Escro, verification gated settlement, and on chain proof,", "words": [{"start": 92.2, "end": 92.68, "word": " Escro,"}, {"start": 92.72, "end": 93.26, "word": " verification"}, {"start": 93.26, "end": 93.7, "word": " gated"}, {"start": 93.7, "end": 94.18, "word": " settlement,"}, {"start": 94.42, "end": 94.56, "word": " and"}, {"start": 94.56, "end": 94.74, "word": " on"}, {"start": 94.74, "end": 95.04, "word": " chain"}, {"start": 95.04, "end": 95.48, "word": " proof,"}]}, {"start": 95.54, "end": 99.04, "text": "all connect through flare with FTC for attestation,", "words": [{"start": 95.54, "end": 95.78, "word": " all"}, {"start": 95.78, "end": 96.1, "word": " connect"}, {"start": 96.1, "end": 96.42, "word": " through"}, {"start": 96.42, "end": 96.76, "word": " flare"}, {"start": 96.76, "end": 97.22, "word": " with"}, {"start": 97.22, "end": 97.56, "word": " FTC"}, {"start": 97.56, "end": 98.02, "word": " for"}, {"start": 98.02, "end": 99.04, "word": " attestation,"}]}, {"start": 100.32, "end": 103.7, "text": "and a T-backed production path for stronger execution guarantees.", "words": [{"start": 100.32, "end": 100.34, "word": " and"}, {"start": 100.34, "end": 100.46, "word": " a"}, {"start": 100.46, "end": 100.64, "word": " T"}, {"start": 100.64, "end": 100.92, "word": "-backed"}, {"start": 100.92, "end": 101.44, "word": " production"}, {"start": 101.44, "end": 101.82, "word": " path"}, {"start": 101.82, "end": 102.1, "word": " for"}, {"start": 102.1, "end": 102.46, "word": " stronger"}, {"start": 102.46, "end": 103.02, "word": " execution"}, {"start": 103.02, "end": 103.7, "word": " guarantees."}]}, {"start": 104.44, "end": 105.94, "text": "And protocol manage wallets.", "words": [{"start": 104.44, "end": 104.72, "word": " And"}, {"start": 104.72, "end": 105.04, "word": " protocol"}, {"start": 105.04, "end": 105.48, "word": " manage"}, {"start": 105.48, "end": 105.94, "word": " wallets."}]}, {"start": 105.94, "end": 108.98, "text": "That is the key shift request to task,", "words": [{"start": 105.94, "end": 106.7, "word": " That"}, {"start": 106.7, "end": 106.96, "word": " is"}, {"start": 106.96, "end": 107.1, "word": " the"}, {"start": 107.1, "end": 107.36, "word": " key"}, {"start": 107.36, "end": 107.88, "word": " shift"}, {"start": 107.88, "end": 108.34, "word": " request"}, {"start": 108.34, "end": 108.64, "word": " to"}, {"start": 108.64, "end": 108.98, "word": " task,"}]}, {"start": 109.24, "end": 111.5, "text": "old funds in escrow, verify the result,", "words": [{"start": 109.24, "end": 109.34, "word": " old"}, {"start": 109.34, "end": 109.62, "word": " funds"}, {"start": 109.62, "end": 109.76, "word": " in"}, {"start": 109.76, "end": 110.38, "word": " escrow,"}, {"start": 110.38, "end": 110.7, "word": " verify"}, {"start": 110.7, "end": 111.04, "word": " the"}, {"start": 111.04, "end": 111.5, "word": " result,"}]}, {"start": 111.96, "end": 114.74, "text": "and record settlement only after the work passes.", "words": [{"start": 111.96, "end": 111.96, "word": " and"}, {"start": 111.96, "end": 112.26, "word": " record"}, {"start": 112.26, "end": 112.74, "word": " settlement"}, {"start": 112.74, "end": 113.56, "word": " only"}, {"start": 113.56, "end": 113.84,